
 The Exit Menu.
 Selecting this menu allows you to do a number of
 miscallaneous things, one of which is to save your screen
 in a selectable format. The rootname of a saved file is
 the same as the current filename in the Status Window and
 the filename extension depends on the format in which you
 are saving.
 Press F6 on the menu items for
 information on those items.

 Keys for the Exit Menu:
	up & down arrows
	CR			select menu item
	F6			help on menu item
	ESC			exit menu
